OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FChilly start with some frost
OL,6,Faround, then bright spells through the
OL,7,Fmorning but cloud thickens through the
OL,8,Fafternoon, perhaps with some patchy
OL,9,Flight rain reaching the Pennines
OL,10,Flater. Winds light but breezy along
OL,11,Fthe coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FOvercast with rain, moderate
OL,14,Fat times spreading eastwards across
OL,15,Fthe region overnight and becoming more
OL,16,Fcontinuous. The wind will gradually
OL,17,Fincrease during the evening become
OL,18,Fmoderate.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
