OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FSaturday, early rain
OL,6,Ffollowed by sunny spells and scattered
OL,7,Fblustery showers. Temperatures mostly
OL,8,Faround average.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday,
OL,11,Fbreezy with occasional blustery
OL,12,Fshowers. Monday, fewer showers and
OL,13,Flighter winds. Tuesday turns more
OL,14,Fsettled with some isolated coastal
OL,15,Fshowers. Temperatures mostly around
OL,16,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
